        <name xml:lang="en">chemical factory, organics</name>
        <unitName xml:lang="en">unit</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">No information was readily available about infrastructure and land-use of cyanoacetic acid production plants. Therefore, in this study, the infrastructure is estimated based on the module "chemical plant, organics". This module assumes a built area of about 4.2 ha, an average output of 50'000 t/a, and plant life of fifty years. For this study, the estimated value is 4.00 E-10 units per kg of produced chemical.
EcoSpold01Location=RER</comment>
